text: Hi there, I've been using the HubSpot CLI for a while now, but today i'm running into an error I haven't seen when running `hs upload` or `hs watch`. It's a syntax error: `Error invoking resize_image_url`. Here is the <https://gist.github.com/jordanderson/eacf85cefbf1e175b9f771a32dea9052|full error> from `hs watch`
the odd thing is that nothing about how i'm calling `resize_image_url` has changed. in fact, i'm pretty sure I successfully uploaded the same files an hour or so ago.
